OL,6,FPeople like "Philip" who now lives in
OL,7,Fa North West safe house run by the
OL,8,FSalvation Army for survivors of modern
OL,9,Fslavery. Young, homeless and a drug
OL,10,Faddict- he felt he had nothing to lose
OL,11,Fwhen he was offered work and a place
OL,12,Fto stay by a friend of a friend. The
OL,13,Fviolence and threats to his life began
OL,14,Falmost immediately.
