OL,6,FPhilip said: "I was stabbed several
OL,7,Ftimes with sharp objects. I was
OL,8,Fattacked with a taser on multiple
OL,9,Foccasions. I had a bottle smashed over
OL,10,Fmy head. I was physically, mentally
OL,11,Fand nearly sexually assaulted every
OL,12,Fday. I was like something out of a
OL,13,Fhorror movie when I managed to get
OL,14,Fout, the police were absolutely
OL,15,Fshocked."
