OL,6,FEmmanuel was trafficked into the UK
OL,7,Ffrom Columbia. His former partner had
OL,8,Fpromised him a better life here.
OL,9,FInstead he was forced to work long
OL,10,Fhours for no pay doing manual labour
OL,11,Fand told he could not leave until he'd
OL,12,Fpaid his trafficker back the money he
OL,13,Fowed.
OL,15,FEmmanuel said: "I had to work all day
OL,16,Fin this house- cleaning, doing the
OL,17,Frepairs, painting the walls and when I
OL,18,Ffinished with that house he hired me
OL,19,Fout to do the same things for other
OL,20,Fpeople. But they paid him and I didn't
OL,21,Fsee any of the money."
