OL,7,Fwas wearing when he was told he'd have
OL,8,Fto start transporting drugs around the
OL,9,Fcountry. He said: "If I see someone on
OL,10,Fthe street who looks like the guy who
OL,11,Fbrought me here- I start to panic.
OL,12,FThat's why I don't look anyone in the
OL,13,Feye anymore. I try to stay away from
OL,14,Fpeople because I don't trust anyone
