OL,6,FVolunteer Deborah Myers teaching
OL,7,Fbaking. She said: "We've found
OL,8,F(survivors) are quite wary to start
OL,9,Fwith, quite withdrawn and it can take
OL,10,Fa couple of years really for them to
OL,11,Fbe able to trust people and build up
OL,12,Ftheir confidence. Our longest survivor
OL,13,Fhas been with us for two years. It's a
OL,14,Fgentle process. A lot of listening to
OL,15,Fthem as well and just being sensitive.
OL,16,FThey know it's a safe space here and
OL,17,Fbaking is a joyful thing to do so
OL,18,Fthat's how it works really."
