OL,6,FJo Rodman, the chair of trustees
OL,7,Fatsaid: "We have had people here who
OL,8,Fhave been physically abused and people
OL,9,Fwho were controlled in a coercive,
OL,10,Femotional control type of way such as
OL,11,Fthreats to their family members for
OL,12,Fexample. We have had people who have
OL,13,Fexperienced torture or held in the sex
OL,14,Findustry and as you can imagine they
OL,15,Fcome to us totally traumatised and so
OL,16,Fwe try to then provide trauma informed
OL,17,Fsympathetic employment to give them a
OL,18,Fhalfway house into the workplace
